{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"id","preciseIdentifier":"c:*Qo","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"init","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(im)init"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/init":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"init","abstract":[],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init","type":"topic"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK":{"title":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.1"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/title","op":"replace","value":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/fragments","op":"replace","value":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/navigatorTitle","op":"replace","value":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]}]}]}